  m_text: 'Navigation:

    ZOOM (Q for In, E for Out), mouse scroll

    ORBIT (Right
    Click)

    PAN (SHIFT + RIGHT CLICK)


    How to Use this Tool:


    Enter
    Coordinates: Type the Latitude and Longitude of your desired location.


    Select
    Vertiport: Use the dropdown to choose your target FATO.


    Generate: Click
    "Show OFV" to start the scan.


    Safety Analysis:


    Green Rays: Clear
    flight paths.


    Red Rays/Cutouts: Blocked by buildings.


    Cyan Arrow:
    Optimal heading based on noise and obstacles.


    Restart: Use the Try new
    location button to try a new location.'
